com.microsoft.azure.storage

Class ResultContinuation

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.azure.storage.ResultContinuation

  • public final class ResultContinuation
extends Object
    Represents a continuation token for listing operations. Continuation tokens are used in methods that return a ResultSegment object, such as CloudBlobDirectory.listBlobsSegmented().
